        <h4 id="changed">Changed:</h4>
        <ul>
        <li>Allow limiting the upload and download bandwidth used for syncing,
        either by setting the config file values, by using the CLI
        <code>maestral bandwidth-limit up|down</code>, or through the Settings
        pane in the GUI.</li>
        <li>Add config file items for the maximum number of parallel file
        transfers.</li>
        <li>Speed up querying the sync status of folders.</li>
        <li>Added support for Python 3.12.</li>
